The blobs were the distorted versions of the pincers.

::::

The bot growls as Repungus admits defeat.

"I'm no Decepticon. I'm an Autobot warrior," he says, instinctively ducking as he hears the roar of missiles. One missile still slams into one of his missile launchers, making him stumble back, the launcher disabled. He fires two missiles from his remaining launcher past Repungus, hoping to hit whatever was there.

> Then a roar of missiles can be heard, as two rockets roar by Repugnas,
> heading for the bum.
